high_descs: Turn around completely and go forward. Turn right and face the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the sink.
Turn and step to the left. Then turn around to the left again and face the oven. Look up to the microwave.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and heat the tomato then take it out.
Turn to the right and walk forward then turn to the right and go around the island. Turn to the right to face the bin.
Place the tomato inside of the bin.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place in a bin.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink.
Pick the tomato up from the sink.
Turn around and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the tomato.
Go left and then left again to face the trash can.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the sink.
Heat the tomato in the microwave then take it out.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter then turn left and walk to the trash can.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the trash.
